\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTsmLsoVUQFIxwmpAJa5v1pXlwGR6sI1jNzFEgdYbIF4YsWO9s=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 years ago\",\"text\":\"One of the best green onion pancake in Taiwan.   The service is fast and pleasant under its pricing range.\",\"time\":1564444146,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"J.David Hwang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108174296883420598113/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk5nrwmgm_vtIuzvcM-PTJC3U-UO1GINfnZzFLZwZckR_K30o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 years ago\",\"text\":\"Despite it’s still very popular, the quality of food is not that good as before.   We had hit & sour soup, green onion pancake, some dumpling and a stir fried side dish.   Mom likes pancake & soup.\",\"time\":1605366710,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Sharon Elmardi\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102694590172374693552/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR3-pxurY1bSTvrcnvEG4vNnFpTDLPpzZSzlurFKGzCHXqqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"a year ago\",\"text\":\"Although this restaurant is famous for it’s dumplings however the stir fried Lou Mei  (Lu Wei) it’s more popular! The scallion pancake was different than the usual kind that you find, it was fresh and tasty.\",\"time\":1704617956,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNSyGiJ6_etfryjpesdBEQaMpnMJLARBAl85MbuYG51T77r5FD6gC33SUc2Y5OgL2FtxhUPz7ey77i6BcjaQ2eXJWdIh5cavr9d-DuW4w9H9jtiJjJxEfijMHtxZBWeDg1fm-n7dX89nEIPa7rJagW6EHapgDaRf72yQa0Cq4xQGgmo3veK9QYdrDMEyhJqpFr6x5QOGrIY2tFGqwmetXbs_w6GLFfNy7u8t1cEBYwIfkmRWzcOMhC1z8tojtnlrBGnFqGyRP6thDq6mVhq9F4OMbZGjXSK1o87V2P6XxfgHL4RhSwIYk01lW59WJ18JtanppEaZ9j8\",\"AXQCQNR31Bclt-omMOUhyA0jFnjGHrCT57Mxs8lFdv_RCqTU4VwW8m