a/ACg8ocKsvRqCFk-Ry85SMMzQTSF6gHtC9B4v5hcQ4BE71ZSdfY3RAg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"7 years ago\",\"text\":\"Italian food that has been mildly altered to fit the taste of Taiwanese population.   The red sauce is not as sour and they cut down on thecampuntcof cheese.   The baked chicken was nice and tender.  The baked chicken penne was good too.\",\"time\":1511698672,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"J.David Hwang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108174296883420598113/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk5nrwmgm_vtIuzvcM-PTJC3U-UO1GINfnZzFLZwZckR_K30o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 years ago\",\"text\":\"Came over here to have a lunch because mom loves their baked cheese seafood rice in pesto sauce.  Somehow, the quantity of salad shrinking a lot (noticeable) but tastes still quite yummy.   I guess it’s an alternative approach on raising the price.\",\"time\":1603686846,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Luka CHOU\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104264312482828291942/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfT5rMupRpnsS9KmA4o74Mg8K1NeGgpa5P17-tLw_6X4jSspU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"a year ago\",\"text\":\"Delicious pasta and pizza. Parking lot is available. Nice place to enjoy Italian food with Friends and Family.\",\"time\":1711940179,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Brendan Scott\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114941291296691114552/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKIOGLi-Dqwdak7P3t7ljkEXxdpDp__WqUIydH9cnAARX0vBHn=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"7 years ago\",\"text\":\"If you've had real Italian food, then 